node.text:
Breathtaking performance with a side of captivating luxury. The #Bentley #ContinentalGT #Mulliner.
_
Model shown is a 2021 model year car which is not available in all markets. Please contact your dealer for availability

node.text:
A Flying Spur unlike anything you've seen before. 

Whether you're behind the wheel experiencing the effortless performance or in the back enjoying the exquisitely crafted cabin, the #FlyingSpur #Mulliner really is one of a kind. 

#BentleyAtMCW21

___

#Bentley Flying Spur Mulliner WLTP drive cycle: fuel consumption, mpg (l/100 km) – Combined 19.1 (14.8). Combined CO₂ – 337 g/km

node.text:
Welcome to the #HomeofBentley at #MontereyCarWeek. 

If you're coming to Monterey, make sure you visit to say hello and take plenty of Bentley pictures. 

Be sure to tag them with #BentleyAtMCW21 so that we can share your great shots with the rest of the #Bentley community around the world.

node.text:
We’re back with a #Bacalar!
 
It’s #MontereyCarWeek and we can’t wait to show you what we have planned, starting with the new Scarab #BentleyMulliner Bacalar. 

If you’re attending the event, come and see it in action this Sunday on the #PebbleConcours Concept Lawn.
 
#BentleyAtMCW21
___

This model is in a preproduction state.
